Package lib.model

Class Meeting

java.lang.Object
lib.model.Grouping
lib.model.Meeting
All Implemented Interfaces:
Has_Copy<Meeting>, Has_ID
public class Meeting extends Grouping implements Has_Copy<Meeting>
A meeting. Similar to group, has interactions, and users can join/leave meetings and post new interactions, but a meeting both has an owning Group and has a specific timestamp and location.

      Object Factory for Meeting Record
      Parameters:
      recordID - primary key can be -1 for null
      ownerID - foreign key to Users table representing ownership of the Meeting. not null

      name - String meeting name
      description - String meeting description
      timestamp - String meeting creation timestamp
      meetingTimestamp - Date the datetime at which the meeting is to take place
